text: Bolshiye Shady () is a rural locality (a village) and the administrative center of Bolsheshadinsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 533 as of 2010. There are 9 streets. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Mishkino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Bolshiye Shady
